{"tid":783000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉非禮案被停職 警員再涉梯間強姦14歲女被捕","createTime":"2018-08-17T08:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T08:33:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":173,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"82124e1fcd71ca5e068ec41b20b321abdadb809e","tid":783000,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"警方毒品調查科一名警員，因早前涉及非禮女童案已被停職受查，惟有人在停職期間，在網上認識了3名女子，上月約同3人到酒吧見面飲酒，飲得興高采烈，稍後有人籍詞送其中一名14歲女童返沙田寓所，並在後樓梯強姦該名女童。<br />\n<br />\n女童稍後返家，被母親發現她有異樣，查問下有人承認曾發生性行為，女童母親大怒報警求助，警方新界北總區重案組接手調查後，昨日拘捕該名停職警員。<br />\n<br />\n涉案警員姓余(32歲)，駐守毒品調查科。據悉，涉案警今年5月在網上社交媒體結識了兩名未成年的援交女，並相約在天水圍區見面，其間涉嫌非禮兩女。警方調查後，於6月在天水圍區拘捕余，他涉嫌「非禮」及「向年齡在16歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為」，其後獲准保釋候查，案件交新界北總區重案組跟進，然而有人在停職期間，再度涉及風化案件而被捕。"},{"pid":"76752de00fa738167b947b9ad8274f8c645123a0","tid":783000,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180817/58575050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58575050&d=jct4TCI%2F8c3l6hKZuz84XkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f42c2445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58575050&h=18196b70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180817/58575050</a>"},{"pid":"f5067ed2883efc973b47729d12091ed34f90134b","tid":783000,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f76cb52b6d1e79aed4588641cd1f98c24da31a","tid":783000,"uid":155818,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"毒品調查科一名警員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01ec3fa54b47b8a98004ce6130acf86d7a3413c","tid":783000,"uid":75137,"lik